Odpowiada za użycie broni rzucanych jak oszczepy, rzutki, kamienie itd.

Strength: Every point adds +1 to hit points. The following skills can not be developed beyond 1/2 of Strength: ironflesh, Power-strike, Power-throw, Power-draw, Inventory Management. Every 5 levels, you get an extra point to add to your attributes.

Agility: Each point gives five weapon points and slightly increases movement speed. The following skills can not be developed beyond 1/2 of Agility: weapon-master, Spotting, Athletics, Riding, Path finding, Looting. Every 5 levels, you get an extra point to add to your attributes.

Intelligence: Every point to intelligence immediately gives one extra skill point. The following skills can not be developed beyond 1/2 of Intelligence: Trainer, Tracking, Tactics, Wound treatment, Surgery, First-aid, Engineer, Navigation, Weapon Maintenance. Every 5 levels, you get an extra point to add to your attributes.

Charisma: Affect in dialogues, seduction and how others see you. Each point increases your party size limit by +1. The following skills can not be developed beyond 1/2 of Charisma: Sea King, Leadership, Persuasion, Trade. Every 5 levels, you get an extra point to add to your attributes.
